  "title": "SALES DESIGNERS",
  "description": "<h3><strong>Job Responsibilities</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Manage and respond to sales enquiries using company-provided quality leads</p></li><li><p>Understand clients’ needs, lifestyle requirements, and renovation expectations</p></li><li><p>Provide professional advice on space planning, design concepts, material selection, and project scheduling</p></li><li><p>Discuss, present, and propose design solutions that meet clients’ needs and budgets</p></li><li><p>Close sales and prepare renovation contracts</p></li><li><p>Coordinate closely with suppliers and contractors to ensure renovation works are completed according to approved plans and timelines</p></li><li><p>Work independently while maintaining strong ownership of assigned projects</p></li></ul><h3><strong>Job Requirements</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Minimum working experience in an <strong>interior design or renovation firm</strong></p></li><li><p>Bilingual: <strong>English</strong> and <strong>Mandarin or Malay</strong></p></li><li><p>Self-driven, motivated, and goal-oriented</p></li><li><p>Responsible, people-oriented, and customer-focused</p></li><li><p>Strong sense of ownership and accountability</p></li></ul>",
