    "description": "<p>Meng Design is established since 1980 and registered under Housing & Development Board with a porfolio of satisfied  customers and their beautifully renovated homes.</p>\n\n<p>We received accreditation from the revelant authorities on our ISO 9001 certification. At Meng Design we just don't strive to just renovate but to create a new atmosphere for everyone.</p>\n\n<p>With a wide range of  designs and materials and highly skill workers at our showrooms & factory, our professional team and dedicated staff is always attentive to assist customers in their individual needs and requirements.</p>\n\n<p>Meng Design & Build provides interior designs, space planning, conceptualise and furnishing services for home, offices and commercial.  At Meng Design, we provide a complete service from applying of renovation permits, bank loans and assisting customers to select suitable furnishings for their homes, thus giving the customers a peace of mind.</p>\n\n<p> </p>\n",
